                            <li>
                                <p> The refreshable Braille display is below the spacebar. </p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <p> While your student is exploring the refreshable Braille display, he or she may place both thumbs down on the thumb-keys to explore them.  The thumb-keys are on the front panel of the BrailleNote.</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <p> The thumb-keys are, starting at the left:</p>
                            
                            <ul>
                                <li>
                                    <p> previous</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
