                    <p>Skills Addressed in this Lesson:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            <p> Enter the User Guide through the Options Menu.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <p> Read the table of contents within the User Guide.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
