                                </li>
                            </ol></li>
                            <li>
                                <p> Exit the User Guide.  Return to the Main Menu.</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <p> From Main Menu, open the User Guide.  At the cue, continue reading about the battery, press n for no.</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <p> At the cue, press t for table of contents.  Use the commands below to read through the table of contents items.</p>
                            
                            <ol>
                                <li>
                                    <p> Space or backspace will move forward and back by item.</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p> Space with e will return to the table of contents.</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
