                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <p> Your student may use the same commands to read the table of contents as he or she did to read the index.</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <p> When your student is finished, return to the Main Menu and turn the BrailleNote off.  Provide time for practice and exploration within the User Guide because it's a great way to learn!</p>
                            </li>
                        </ol>
                    </subsection>
