                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <p> Use space or the advance thumb-key to explore the areas of the keylist menu.  These choices include add address, look up address, copy addresses, emboss addresses, print addresses, select keylist file, and free database space.</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
