                                    <p> Middle name</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p> Title</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p> Home phone number</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p> Business phone number</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p> Cell phone number</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p> Home e-mail address</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p> Business e-mail address</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p> Home fax number</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p> Business fax number</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p> Street address</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p> City</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p> State</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p> Zip or postal code</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p> State</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p> Country</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p> Business title</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p> Company name</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p> Department</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p> Business street address</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p> Business state</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p> Business zip</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p> Business country</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p> Web page</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p> Notes</p>
                                </li>
                            </ol></li>
                            <li>
                                <p> When your student has entered information in the appropriate fields, he or she can press e with space. When prompted to "add record?" key in y and press enter.</p>
                            </li>
