                        <title>Deleting Files</title>
                        <p>For practice, delete any file as follows:</p>
                        <p>From the Main menu, press F, then Enter, to open the File Manager.</p>
                        <p>Press Enter to Open Storage.</p>
                        <p>Press D until you get to Documents, then press Enter.</p>
                        <p>Choose a file to delete.</p>
                        <p>Press Backspace+dots2356; you will be asked if you want to delete the file.</p>
                        <p>Press O for OK, then Enter to delete the file.</p>
                    </subsection>
